Engine / MLX work in this repo. See [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) for architecture and Known traps.

## Mandatory (substantive changes, not typos)

Launch **`concurrency-auditor`** and **`memory-auditor`** via `Task` before merging engine diffs.

## Skills

- `swift-mlx`, `swift-mlx-lm` for MLX array/runtime/generation internals
- `axiom:axiom-performance` for slow paths, RSS, streaming bench forensics

## Validation

- `./scripts/build.sh debug`
- Streaming / event-buffer changes → bench gate in [`docs/reference/bench-agent-gate.md`](../../docs/reference/bench-agent-gate.md)

## CRITICAL invariants (do not regress)

- macOS `MLXTTSEngine.events` stays **`.unbounded`** (iOS may use `.bufferingNewest(64)`)
- Prewarm **reentrancy gate** (`acquirePrewarmSlot` / `releasePrewarmSlot`) must stay serialized
- **Generation ownership** — one model-mutating operation at a time; streaming producers must cancel on stream termination

Playbook: [`.cursor/rules/vocello-agent-playbook.mdc`](vocello-agent-playbook.mdc)
